{"tid":258924,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點解電話用電咁快","createTime":"2017-05-26T13:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T10:20:23.000Z","uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae315e9c3f19f69af55ae9ee9d0239a9e8fbbc76","tid":258924,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/213849_29459fa42692faea25ff7d7c4950249e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F213849_29459fa42692faea25ff7d7c4950249e.jpg&h=609bb937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n換左新電都係咁 以為電問題今日換多舊都係咁<br />\nWhatsapp 係背景個問題應該搵到，解決左whatsapp個個但都係用好快<br />\n電話係6s 用左一年幾，以前舊電勁耐用，我9x%訓，訓醒都係扣得幾%(開住data gps),而家訓醒得返3x%<br />\n求幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939c835e863cccb7f4f9e5b8a6a5b4042cdf8585","tid":258924,"uid":74329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"個mon較得太光？"},{"pid":"659de151fbdb67e0aac5b8c0dc99ab198e98d04f","tid":258924,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個mon較得太光？</blockquote><br />\n由最初用電話已經用auto-brightness<br />\n平時變太光都會手動較返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf6389844a1f558416e0aad03735e9acf719090","tid":258924,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"個ios剛剛裝？"},{"pid":"b2532e5b0b3f23596ff3f139884fd1ef66f04790","tid":258924,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"個whatsapp 係背景run係好撚食電，一定要kill左佢先得"},{"pid":"a4c71a933d86f87fa203fd0244ef2dd8298d6253","tid":258924,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個ios剛剛裝？</blockquote><br />\n琴日升左10.3.2 一直都係更新無重新裝過無restore過"},{"pid":"9dc5e37f0fd5b17d39ea8004a38fb7